Objectives
The framework supports:

objective performance assessment;
evidence-based engineering decisions;
statistical interpretation of monitoring data;
transparent technical reporting;
reproducible analytical workflows.

Core Topics
Future sections will include:

performance indicators;
statistical summaries;
treatment reliability;
uncertainty analysis;
data visualization;
reproducible reporting;
engineering interpretation;
best practices.

Website Roadmap
This site will gradually include:

treatment performance assessment frameworks;
engineering statistics tutorials;
reproducible Quarto, R, and Python workflows;
public research and publications;
teaching and mentoring resources;
reviews of methods, tools, and technical resources.
